<li>Formal navy doctrine suffered a setback with the introduction of new technologies and the end of the Anglo-Franco wars in the Nineteenth Century; 
<li>Pre-war military doctrine cannot forseee all eventualities; 
<li>Centralized military doctrine should not be cast in stone; 
